description.en: IQeon is the first platform where players can earn money thanks to their intelligence and achievements. This will be realized by using the internal currency in the IQeon ecosystem, which at any time can be converted to the crypto currency – IQeon tokens (IQN) issued based on Ethereum blockchain. IQeon tokens (IQN) can be freely exchanged at existing cryptocurrency exchanges, or transferred to fiat money.

This will be realized by using the internal currency in the IQeon ecosystem, which at any time can be converted to the crypto currency – IQeon tokens (IQN) issued based on Ethereum blockchain. IQeon tokens (IQN) can be freely exchanged at existing cryptocurrency exchanges, or transferred to fiat money on a MasterCard card thanks to the established partnership with Loyal Bank Limited.

status_updates.description:
🤝Introducing the new IQeon partner – PlayToEarn – the first ever portal that generated a rating of games on the blockchain!

IQeon.com gaming platform already takes its place in the list of top crypto solutions🏆 And we are very glad that now even more enthusiasts will be able to evaluate its strengths!
 
Read more https://bit.ly/3omiYSc

🔥IQeon CMO will take part in the international online event Open Web Community Summit 2021!

On May 14, the founders and developers of well-known platforms, as well as artists and supporters of digitalization, will share their experience of interacting with non-fungible and social tokens, as well as decentralized autonomous organizations, and will discuss the prospects for virtual worlds and social tokenomics development. It will be interesting😉

Read more https://bit.ly/2

⚙️IQeon development report for the period from April 14 to May 11, 2021

🔺Improved user data protection 
🔺Optimized the speed of loading pages on IQeon.com website
🔺Localized blocks of the gaming platform into Chinese
🔺Improved algorithm of the Telegram bot, which accrues bonus IQN

Read more https://bit.ly/3uIp4yO

🚀Summing up the results of April!

✅Rewarding the best platform players
✅Results of Games Marathon contest
✅Launch of IQeon products localization
✅Partnership with CoinSpeaker portal
✅IQeon.com platform update

Read more https://bit.ly/3mZCoeY

🚀Introducing the new IQeon partner – CoinSpeaker media resource about finance, blockchain and cryptocurrency!
 
Thanks to the collaboration with this high-profile portal, IQeon project will be able to expand its influence in the info space and attract more talented players to IQeon.com PvP platform.

Read more https://bit.ly/3dZnqlg

⚙️IQeon development report for the period from March 10 to April 12, 2021

🔺Optimized player's personal profile
🔺Improved IQeon.com language versions 
🔺Eliminated bugs in the games module
🔺Fixed defects in the display of platform blocks

Read more https://bit.ly/3scG2Dn

🏁Friends, the final stage of Games Marathon is coming soon!

The third round of the gaming battle will be held on IQeon.com platform from April 12 to 18. Everyone who keeps going and shows their endurance for another seven days of the marathon will rightfully receive the biggest prize of the competition – 10 IQN!

Play at least one match per day for a week and get a well-deserved reward!🔥

Read more about the third stage at IQeon.io https://bit.ly/3fWwkSU
